WEBVTT

00:00:01.600 --> 00:00:03.536
I am British.

00:00:03.560 --> 00:00:05.696
(Laughter)

00:00:05.720 --> 00:00:08.856
(Applause)

00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:12.656
Never before has the phrase
"I am British" elicited so much pity.

00:00:12.680 --> 00:00:14.776
(Laughter)

00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:17.536
I come from an island
where many of us like to believe

00:00:17.560 --> 00:00:20.680
there's been a lot of continuity
over the last thousand years.

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:24.136
We tend to have historically
imposed change on others

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:26.480
but done much less of it ourselves.

00:00:27.360 --> 00:00:29.816
So it came as an immense shock to me

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:32.616
when I woke up on the morning of June 24